===Usage notes===
Note that the pronunciation differs depending on register, which also happens for the antonym "[[yesterday]]" and the coordinate term "[[today]]". Corresponding in formality to ''ashita'', ''asu'', and ''myōnichi'' for "tomorrow" are {{ja-l|昨日||kinō}}, {{ja-l|昨日||kiso|pos=rare}}, and {{ja-l|昨日||sakujitsu}} for "yesterday"; and {{ja-l|今日||kyō}},{{ja-l|今日||konnichi}}, and {{ja-l|本日||honjutsu}} for "today".

